<h3 class='datestamp'>25 February 2017</h3>
<div id="p-606004" class="p18 post publish id606004 a-ndesanjo-macha y2017 m02 d25 h07 alt post-summary post-summary-thumbnail">
 	 <div class='post-summary-content'><a href="https://globalvoices.org/2017/02/25/you-can-now-nominate-candidates-for-the-2017-kenya-blog-awards/" title="Read this post"><div class='thumbnail-container css-thumbnail-container  featured-image-container'><div title='Read this post' class='css-post-thumbnail  post-featured-image' style='background-image: url(https://globalvoices.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Bake-awards-2016-400x300.jpg)'></div></div></a><div class='post-excerpt-container'><h3 class="post-title"> <a href="https://globalvoices.org/2017/02/25/you-can-now-nominate-candidates-for-the-2017-kenya-blog-awards/" title="You Can Now Nominate Candidates for the 2017 Kenya Blog Awards" rel="bookmark">You Can Now Nominate Candidates for the 2017 Kenya Blog Awards</a></h3> 
 	<div class='postmeta post-summary-postmeta-top'>
 	 <span class="credit-text"><span class='contributor'>Written by&nbsp;<a href="https://globalvoices.org/author/ndesanjo-macha/" class="url user-link" title="View all posts by Ndesanjo Macha">Ndesanjo Macha</a></span></span> &middot; <span class='post-terms-inline'><a href='https://globalvoices.org/-/world/sub-saharan-africa/' rel='tag' title="Show posts about Sub-Saharan Africa">Sub-Saharan Africa</a></span><!--.post-terms-inline--></div> <!--.postmeta-->
<div class="entry excerpt-entry">
<p class='excerpt-text'>The Kenyan Blog Awards is now taking submissions for this year's ceremony. The call for nominations runs until March 10. Bloggers and fans can submit nominations in several different categories.</p>
</div><!--.entry--> 
 </div></div></div><div id="p-605990" class="p19 post publish id605990 a-ndesanjo-macha y2017 m02 d25 h06 post-summary post-summary-thumbnail">
 	 <div class='post-summary-content'><a href="https://globalvoices.org/2017/02/25/new-clashes-over-immigrants-sweep-south-africa/" title="Read this post"><div class='thumbnail-container css-thumbnail-container  featured-image-container'><div title='Read this post' class='css-post-thumbnail  post-featured-image' style='background-image: url(https://globalvoices.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Peoples_March_Anti_Xenophobia-400x300.jpg)'></div></div></a><div class='post-excerpt-container'><h3 class="post-title"> <a href="https://globalvoices.org/2017/02/25/new-clashes-over-immigrants-sweep-south-africa/" title="New Clashes Over Immigrants Sweep South Africa" rel="bookmark">New Clashes Over Immigrants Sweep South Africa</a></h3> 
 	<div class='postmeta post-summary-postmeta-top'>
 	 <span class="credit-text"><span class='contributor'>Written by&nbsp;<a href="https://globalvoices.org/author/ndesanjo-macha/" class="url user-link" title="View all posts by Ndesanjo Macha">Ndesanjo Macha</a></span></span> &middot; <span class='post-terms-inline'><a href='https://globalvoices.org/-/world/sub-saharan-africa/' rel='tag' title="Show posts about Sub-Saharan Africa">Sub-Saharan Africa</a></span><!--.post-terms-inline--></div> <!--.postmeta-->
<div class="entry excerpt-entry">
<p class='excerpt-text'>South Africa is currently in the midst of another wave of attacks against African immigrants, with crowds shouting xenophobic slogans and looting and burning down businesses and homes.</p>
</div><!--.entry--> 
 </div></div></div><div id="p-605884" class="p20 post publish id605884 a-pri y2017 m02 d25 h10 alt post-summary post-summary-thumbnail">
 	 <div class='post-summary-content'><a href="https://globalvoices.org/2017/02/25/us-activists-on-overdrive-to-respond-to-trumps-immigration-plans-are-making-new-alliances/" title="Read this post"><div class='thumbnail-container css-thumbnail-container  featured-image-container'><div title='Read this post' class='css-post-thumbnail  post-featured-image' style='background-image: url(https://globalvoices.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ASHA-protesting--400x300.jpg)'></div></div></a><div class='post-excerpt-container'><h3 class="post-title"> <a href="https://globalvoices.org/2017/02/25/us-activists-on-overdrive-to-respond-to-trumps-immigration-plans-are-making-new-alliances/" title="US Activists, on Overdrive to Respond to Trump’s Immigration Plans, Are Making New Alliances" rel="bookmark">US Activists, on Overdrive to Respond to Trump’s Immigration Plans, Are Making New Alliances</a></h3> 
 	<div class='postmeta post-summary-postmeta-top'>
 	 <span class="credit-text"><span class='contributor'>Written by&nbsp;<a href="https://globalvoices.org/author/pri/" class="url user-link" title="View all posts by PRI/PRX's The World">PRI/PRX's The World</a></span></span> &middot; <span class='post-terms-inline'><a href='https://globalvoices.org/-/world/north-america/' rel='tag' title="Show posts about North America">North America</a></span><!--.post-terms-inline--></div> <!--.postmeta-->
<div class="entry excerpt-entry">
<p class='excerpt-text'>“Even before I shower, my mailbox is almost full. And soon as I wake up my phone starts ringing,” says Detroit organizer Adonis Flores.</p>
